  <summary date="2020-05-26T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Fairness for Early Withdrawers Act

This bill allows tax-preferred pension plan participants to recontribute distributions from such plans made prior to December 1, 2020, without regard to the 60-day rule that requires a rollover of distributions to another plan within 60 days after receipt of such distributions.</summary>
